<subSubSection id="C3037492FFB1FF99E0842B7E22E9B9E5" pageId="12" pageNumber="89" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BA62719FFB1FF99E0842B7E22E9B9E5" blockId="12.[151,1436,429,672]" pageId="12" pageNumber="89">
<emphasis id="B96DFB0BFFB1FF99E0842B7E2757B971" bold="true" box="[199,317,538,564]" pageId="12" pageNumber="89">Remarks:</emphasis>
It is unclear whether these records refer to the subspecies 
<taxonomicName id="4C195C9AFFB1FF99E3FC2B7F22EDB971" authority="hirsuta" authorityName="hirsuta - A. M. Clark" authorityYear="1968" box="[959,1159,538,564]" class="Ophiuroidea" family="Ophiotrichidae" genus="Macrophiothrix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ophiurida" pageId="12" pageNumber="89" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="subSpecies" species="hirsuta" subSpecies="hirsuta">
<emphasis id="B96DFB0BFFB1FF99E3FC2B7F25BCB971" box="[959,982,539,564]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="89">M</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B96DFB0BFFB1FF99E3A02B7E22EDB971" box="[995,1159,538,564]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="89">hirsuta hirsuta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
or to 
<taxonomicName id="4C195C9AFFB1FF99E4852B7F23FFB971" authorityName="Lyman" authorityYear="1861" box="[1222,1429,538,564]" class="Ophiuroidea" family="Ophiotrichidae" genus="Macrophiothrix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ophiurida" pageId="12" pageNumber="89" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="subSpecies" species="hirsuta" subSpecies="cheneyi">
<emphasis id="B96DFB0BFFB1FF99E4852B7F22B7B971" box="[1222,1245,539,564]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="89">M</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B96DFB0BFFB1FF99E4A82B7E23FFB971" box="[1259,1429,538,564]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="89">hirsuta cheneyi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, because none of the authors considered 
<taxonomicName id="4C195C9AFFB1FF99E20D2B5A25D7B91D" authority="Lyman, 1861" authorityName="Lyman" authorityYear="1861" box="[590,957,574,600]" class="Ophiuroidea" family="Ophiotrichidae" genus="Ophiothrix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ophiurida" pageId="12" pageNumber="89" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="cheneyi">
<emphasis id="B96DFB0BFFB1FF99E20D2B5A254FB91D" box="[590,805,574,600]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="89">Ophiothrix cheneyi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF885AE8FFB1FF99E3692B5A25D7B91D" author="Lyman, T." box="[810,957,574,600]" pageId="12" pageNumber="89" pagination="75 - 86" refId="ref16311" refString="Lyman, T. (1861) Descriptions of new Ophiuridae. Proceedings of the Boston Society of Natural History 1859 - 61, 8, 75 - 86. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. part. 10220" type="journal article" year="1861">
Lyman, 
<quantity id="4CE18AFCFFB1FF99E3C62B5A25D7B91D" box="[901,957,574,600]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.72694" pageId="12" pageNumber="89" unit="in" value="1861.0">1861</quantity>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
in their comments. The subspecific separation and inclusion of 
<taxonomicName id="4C195C9AFFB1FF99E1C62B062797B939" authorityName="Lyman" authorityYear="1861" box="[389,509,610,636]" class="Ophiuroidea" family="Ophiotrichidae" genus="Ophiothrix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ophiurida" pageId="12" pageNumber="89" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="cheneyi">
<emphasis id="B96DFB0BFFB1FF99E1C62B0627F3B939" box="[389,409,610,636]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="89">O</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B96DFB0BFFB1FF99E1E42B062797B939" box="[423,509,610,636]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="89">cheneyi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<taxonomicName id="4C195C9AFFB1FF99E2632B0624BAB939" authorityName="H. L. Clark" authorityYear="1938" box="[544,720,610,636]" class="Ophiuroidea" family="Ophiotrichidae" genus="Macrophiothrix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ophiurida" pageId="12" pageNumber="89" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96DFB0BFFB1FF99E2632B0624BAB939" box="[544,720,610,636]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="89">Macrophiothrix</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was proposed by A. M. 
<bibRefCitation id="EF885AE8FFB1FF99E3A22B062219B938" author="Clark, A. M." box="[993,1139,610,637]" pageId="12" pageNumber="89" pagination="275 - 322" refId="ref14057" refString="Clark, A. M. (1968) Notes on some tropical Indo-Pacific ophiotrichids and ophiodermatids (Ophiuroidea). Bulletin of the British Museum (Natural History), 16, 275 - 322." type="journal article" year="1968">Clark (1968)</bibRefCitation>
, but she continued to refer to 
<taxonomicName id="4C195C9AFFB1FF99E0F72BE32742B9E5" baseAuthorityName="Muller &amp; Troschel" baseAuthorityYear="1842" box="[180,296,646,672]" class="Ophiuroidea" family="Ophiotrichidae" genus="Macrophiothrix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ophiurida" pageId="12" pageNumber="89" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="hirsuta">
<emphasis id="B96DFB0BFFB1FF99E0F72BE326A1B9E5" box="[180,203,647,672]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="89">M</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B96DFB0BFFB1FF99E09A2BE22742B9E5" box="[217,296,646,672]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="89">hirsuta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
without subspecific distinction (
<bibRefCitation id="EF885AE8FFB1FF99E2D52BE225EEB9E5" author="Clark, A. M. &amp; Taylor, J. D." box="[662,900,646,672]" pageId="12" pageNumber="89" pagination="89 - 92" refId="ref14341" refString="Clark, A. M. &amp; Taylor, J. D. (1971) Echinoderms from Diego Garcia. Atoll Research Bulletin, 149, 89 - 92." type="journal article" year="1971">Clark &amp; Taylor 1971</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EF885AE8FFB1FF99E3D32BE2221CB9E5" author="Clark, A. M. &amp; Rowe, F. W. E." box="[912,1142,646,672]" pageId="12" pageNumber="89" refId="ref14301" refString="Clark, A. M. &amp; Rowe, F. W. E. (1971) Monograph of Shallow-water Indo-west Pacific Echinoderms. Trustees of the British Museum (Natural History), London, 234 pp." type="book" year="1971">Clark &amp; Rowe 1971</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
